      <portrait>Esbenus</portrait>
      <speaker_name />
      <npc_text>"I told this story many times and each time I wonder why I didn't immediately take my men and flee. It seems so obvious now, but back then, in that chamber, we felt like we had stepped into a fairy tale. It was a tale rife with disappearing walls, strange idols, and magic carts taking only the worthy to hidden treasures beyond their wildest dreams. I sent my best men to see what was down there and bring back Nicanor. None of them returned.

"When the platform came back, it was as if it had come back for us. We ran outside to clear our minds and to escape from the hidden evils of that place."</npc_text>
